{"tid":923081,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Iphone xr 比Iphone x 好","createTime":"2018-12-01T03:00:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-01T13:50:02.000Z","uid":175335,"like":16,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"59c79b1186d5eb64305dace8c0c82a638885c59a","tid":923081,"uid":175335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T03:00:08.000Z","msg":"本身用緊 iphone 7 plus ，見iphone都已經出左兩代，開始心思思想試下新嘅iphone。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無奈本身budget唔多，早幾日唯有係某購物網站Caxxll 用6000蚊買左部有保養嘅iphone x 256g。交收時發現嗰靜音掣有啲鬆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，過咗幾日去apple store 換咗部翻新機。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （6000蚊買部官方翻新機，都唔蝕。等於免費幫你check 過部機一次同換埋電池。）apple 售後就係好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n用咗一個星期之後，覺得face id 完勝 touch id，嗰種方便程度完全係另外一個層次。至於部機size就比iphone 7plus 細，雖然話個mon大過7plus，但係用落都係覺得細啲，有啲唔慣。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁啱我同事最近又出咗部 白色 iphone xr，咁即刻攞嚟比較吓。<br />\n1，外形：啲人成日話xr 條邊框好粗，但係望落部白色 xr 條邊框又唔算好粗，望落都係可以接受。至於其他色，之前係百x匯睇過，完全唔可以接受，呢個都係導致我點解唔買xr 買 x 嘅原因。<br />\n2，Mon ：雖然話iphone x 用 OLED，xr 用Liquid LED Mon。係youtube搵4K片播嚟比較，完全睇唔出有乜分別。幾個人睇完都係咁講。另外iphone xr個mon比iphone x大，令我有用翻7 plus 嘅感覺到。<br />\n3.相機：相機遠景差唔多，近景iphone x多咗個鏡頭就唔使試都知。<br />\n最後如果俾我揀多一次，會唔會買翻xr<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，真係幾難揀。"},{"pid":"3ea60dbf87877849ae6e5cb51e09781e38531a55","tid":923081,"uid":21423,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T03:00:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b35082d537a30e46a7c2d104c958fd652e768cf3","tid":923081,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T03:04:01.000Z","msg":"仲使講，淨係舊電好咁多已經贏晒！無電話之你識飛"},{"pid":"0e31936590d813b8ffa5515f417fe1067748c539","tid":923081,"uid":21423,"like":2,"dislike":9,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T03:06:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d76a794025a0fbee1be7c9e4113912b0e42209e7","tid":923081,"uid":12628,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T03:10:54.000Z","msg":"請大家唔理上面條搞事肥傻鳩，繼續正常討論就得喇"},{"pid":"2321d194cf9bb580233d11f349ca022246cedee8","tid":923081,"uid":159448,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T03:15:07.000Z","msg":"完全封鎖我只係封左1個 唔通係佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3bfd2780a7ececd969e570084c8e7fd5c456e1e","tid":923081,"uid":95172,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T03:23:51.000Z","msg":"iphone係好野,  oh , 好好野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3c9e4f6f92c6453768138da1071bef2c82f5983","tid":923081,"uid":60605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T03:28:37.000Z","msg":"係，所以我由x轉xr，果時喺HABBITZZ 五千五執到部，但係部x賣唔出，唯有比屋企人用"},{"pid":"36e0da4374cfeb57c49fd5a34fd4d40a74ad7dc2","tid":923081,"uid":175335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d3c9e4f6f92c6453768138da1071bef2c82f5983","tid":923081,"uid":60605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T03:28:37.000Z","msg":"係，所以我由x轉xr，果時喺HABBITZZ 五千五執到部，但係部x賣唔出，唯有比屋企人用"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T04:08:06.000Z","msg":"你幾多G？64通常5000幾，256就有6000"},{"pid":"a66f5b290eebe56903038765321e4c75b4cd9c01","tid":923081,"uid":175335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e3bfd2780a7ececd969e570084c8e7fd5c456e1e","tid":923081,"uid":95172,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T03:23:51.000Z","msg":"iphone係好野,  oh , 好好野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T04:08:19.000Z","msg":"售後冇得頂"},{"pid":"e39797b9e7fbbbc4eda1e9fee5dbb5d1511e3edd","tid":923081,"uid":175335,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b35082d537a30e46a7c2d104c958fd652e768cf3","tid":